definition: starting an automobile engine that has a weak battery by means of jumper cables to another car, start or re-start vigorously
details:
noun
- starting an automobile engine that has a weak battery by means of jumper cables to another car
= synonyms: jumpstart
verb
- start or re-start vigorously
= synonyms: jumpstart
- start (a car engine whose battery is dead) by connecting it to another car's battery
= synonyms: jump, jumpstart
